{"id":27,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":27,"title":"Chapter 24: Ammon Meets King Lamoni’s Father","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 24"],["h1","Ammon Meets King Lamoni’s Father"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p3"},"King Lamoni wanted to take Ammon to meet his father. The Lord warned Ammon not to go because Lamoni’s father would try to kill him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.1-2"},"Alma 20:1–2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p5"},"The Lord told Ammon to go instead to the land of Middoni, where his brother Aaron was in prison. King Lamoni went with Ammon."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.2-4"},"Alma 20:2–4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p7"},"As they traveled they met King Lamoni’s father, who was king over all the land. He asked Lamoni where he was going with a lying Nephite."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.8,10"},"Alma 20:8, 10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p9"},"King Lamoni told his father about Ammon and his brother who was in prison. Angry, Lamoni’s father ordered Lamoni to kill Ammon and not go to Middoni."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.11-14"},"Alma 20:11–14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p11"},"Lamoni refused to kill Ammon and said he and Ammon were going to free Aaron. Lamoni’s father became angrier and drew his sword to kill Lamoni."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.15-16"},"Alma 20:15–16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p13"},"Ammon stepped forward to protect Lamoni. Lamoni’s father then tried to kill Ammon, but he defended himself and wounded the arm of Lamoni’s father."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.17,20"},"Alma 20:17, 20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p15"},"When Lamoni’s father saw that Ammon could kill him, he offered Ammon half of his kingdom if he would spare his life."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.21,23"},"Alma 20:21, 23"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p17"},"Ammon said he wanted Aaron and his companions freed from prison and wanted Lamoni to be able to keep his kingdom."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.22,24"},"Alma 20:22, 24"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p19"},"Lamoni’s father realized that Ammon did not want to hurt him. He was amazed at how much Ammon loved his son. He invited Ammon to teach him the gospel."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.26-27"},"Alma 20:26–27"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p21"},"Ammon and King Lamoni went to Middoni. Lamoni spoke with the king there, and Aaron and his companions were released from prison."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.28"},"Alma 20:28"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_027_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p23"},"Ammon was sad to see how poorly they had been treated. They had suffered much but had been patient."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-24-ammon-meets-king-lamonis-father.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/20.29"},"Alma 20:29"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
